text: Je l'ai un peu caché. C'est un vieux tableau. This one is pretty old.
translation: I hid it a little bit. It's an old painting. This one is pretty old.

text: I can tell you, in the Twentieth Century.
translation: I can tell you, in the Twentieth Century.

text: Alors, tu vois, je faisais la mer alors, et je fais la mer encore maintenant.
translation: So, you see, I was doing the sea then, and I'm still doing the sea now.

text: Quelle mer ? Je sais pas, ça. C'est plutôt la mer du Nord.
translation: Which sea?  I don't know.  It's probably the North Sea.
